snippet.title: TEKKEN Tag Tournament 2 Wii U Edition - Wii U - Tekken does Wii U
snippet.description:
The Tekken Tag Tournament 2 family extends with the addition of the Wii U edition.
Nintendo fans will jump in the action in November 2012 with a special version of the game including new exclusive features for the Nintendo Wii U™ console.

For more information, join the community on http://www.facebook.com/tekken or visit the official website on http://www.tekken.com
